		<div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
			<p class="show-text">
				Varna Necropolis is a burial site outside of Varna area that has the oldest gold treasure in the world dating back 6,000 years. Since it’s discovery in 1972 more than 3,000 pieces of ancient gold has been found in this ancient burial site.


			</p>
		</div>
		
		
		
		<div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
			<figure>
